      <rules>
        <rule id="628f-efa1-b36a-f1c8" name="Ogre Bodyguard" hidden="false">
          <description>Upkeep 30gc
Rating +25 (+1/exp)
Weapons/Armour: Either two swords, axes or clubs (or any mix of them), or a double-handed weapon (you may choose which). Ogres wear light armour.

May be Hired: Any warband except Skaven may hire an Ogre Bodyguard.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
