      <rules>
        <rule id="baf8-e01d-b2bd-b348" name="Freelancer" hidden="false">
          <description>Upkeep: 20gc
Rating: +21 (+1/exp)
Equipment: Heavy armour, shield, lance and sword

May be Hired: Mercenaries and Witch Hunters may hire Freelancers.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="553f-0ede-d99c-825f" name="Freelancer Mount" hidden="false">
          <description>If you are using the optional rules for mounted models, a Freelancer rides a warhorse (and has the Ride Warhorse skill from the Blazing Saddles article).

When mounted, the Freelancer has an armour saving throw of 3+. On foot his save is 4+.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
