      <rules>
        <rule id="c4b9-e0ac-9f97-c7c2" name="Warlock" hidden="false">
          <description>Upkeep: 15gc
Rating: +16 (+1/exp)

Warlocks are magicians and have two spells generated at random from the Lesser Magic list. See the Magic section for details. 

May be Hired: Any warband except Witch Hunters and Sisters of Sigmar may hire a Warlock.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
