      <rules>
        <rule id="e98b-7541-04a1-097f" name="Tilean Marksman" hidden="false">
          <description>May be Hired: Any warband except Skaven, Orcs or Undead may hire the Tilean Marksman.

30 gold crowns to hire + 15 gold crowns upkeep.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="eea6-7d8d-c3d5-b979" name="Steady Hands" hidden="false">
          <description>The Tilean Marksman&apos;s aim never wavers.

He ignores &apos;to hit&apos; modifiers for long range when shooting his crossbow.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="3c95-da05-7e75-6f0f" name="Dead Eye Shot" hidden="false">
          <description>The Marksman has the eyes of an eagle and can hit the smallest target.
He ignores &apos;to hit&apos; modifiers for cover when shooting his crossbow.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
