      <rules>
        <rule id="06d8-eb4a-6a26-274b" name="Big Game Hunter" hidden="false">
          <description>May be Hired: The Big Game Hunter can be hired by any human Warband.

40 gold crowns to hire + 18 gold crowns upkeep.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="cf77-40ef-2b21-3fd4" name="Set Traps" hidden="false">
          <description>The Hunter may place up to six counters to represent these traps on the board immediately after the Hunter model is placed.

They must be placed at ground level with at least 6&quot; between them.

Any model (except the Hunter) that moves within 3&quot; of a trap counter must roll a D6.
  On a 1-3, nothing happens.
  On a 4-6, the model takes a single hit automatically at the strength shown on the dice.

The trap counter is then removed.

A single model can only set off one trap at a time.
If an animal of any sort is put Out of Action by a trap, it is automatically captured after the game to be sent to the Old World .</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
