      <rules>
        <rule id="e8fc-6919-1d08-1945" name="Elf Ranger" hidden="false">
          <description>Upkeep: 20gc
Rating: +12pts (+1/exp)
May be Hired: Mercenaries and Witch Hunters may hire Elf Rangers. Warbands which include Dwarfs may hire Elf Rangers, but must pay 40 gold crowns after each battle instead of 20.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="6de2-5c61-4e53-5fa7" name="Excellent Sight" hidden="false">
          <description>The Elf Ranger spots Hidden enemies from two times as far away as other warriors (ie, twice his Initiative value in inches).</description>
        </rule>
        <rule id="58bf-a0ec-c5c1-100a" name="Seeker" hidden="false">
          <description>When rolling on the Exploration chart, the Elf Ranger allows you to modify one dice roll by -1/+1.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
